description: Takes brand names from uploaded CSV, researches each brand on the web to collect: website URL, logo URL, founded year, about us summary, product category (e.g., consumer tech, sportswear), social media links (Twitter, LinkedIn, Instagram, Facebook), and contact info (email, phone, HQ address). Returns structured data with "Not Found" for unavailable fields.

brands.website_url: Official website URL or Not Found
brands.logo_url: URL to the brand logo or Not Found
brands.founded_year: Year the brand was founded or Not Found
brands.about_summary: 2-3 sentence about us summary or Not Found
brands.product_category: Brand category e.g. Consumer Tech, Sportswear or Not Found

social_media.twitter: Twitter/X profile URL or Not Found
social_media.linkedin: LinkedIn page URL or Not Found
social_media.instagram: Instagram profile URL or Not Found
social_media.facebook: Facebook page URL or Not Found

brands.status: Complete if all fields found, Partial if some Not Found
